model_description: Using the clustering method outlined in https://arxiv.org/abs/2110.01183, we use each account's distribution of images across political-image clusters as features for classification.
Take the mean image embedding for all images from an account and predict directly on this embedded structure.
Baseline that predicts a random value for authenticity and a random campaign for disinfo agents
Baseline that predicts the most common label, which is no disinformation agent.
